Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Cholesterol-free Christmas, anyone?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xgcw
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 23 Dec 1984
Keep cutting your cholesterol, say the experts - just as the Christmas eating binge beckons. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less